content: I remember that I stayed at the Yarrow Hotel with my friends Alex and Rachel, and we had a blast exploring the festival's venues and trying out different restaurants and cafes in the area. That must have been during Sundance 2022. So, I did attend Sundance 2022, and I saw 12 films, including "Minari" and "The French Dispatch" wasn't one of them. Can you help me figure out the other 10 films I saw?
